		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about the country. For the island, see <a href="Hispaniola" title="Hispaniola">Hispaniola</a>. For other uses, see <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haiti_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Haiti (disambiguation)">Haiti (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Hayti" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hayti_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Hayti (disambiguation)">Hayti (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Country in the Caribbean</div>
<p>
