hnic&#160;groups</a> <div style="font-weight:normal;display:inline;"></div></th><td>95% <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afro-Haitians" title="Afro-Haitians">black</a><br />5% <small><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mulatto_Haitians" title="Mulatto Haitians">mixed</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/White_Haitians" title="White Haitians">white</a></small><sup id="cite_ref-CIA_20110303_4-0" class="reference"><a href="Haiti#cite_note-CIA_20110303-4">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope="row"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Demonym" title="Demonym">Demonym(s)</a></th><td><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haitians" title="Haitians">Haitian</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Politics_of_Haiti" title="Politics of Haiti">Government</a></th><td><span class="nowrap"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unitary_state" title="Unitary state">Unitary</a> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Semi-presidential_republic" class="mw-redirect" title="Semi-presidential republic">semi-presidential</a></span> <a href="Republic" title="Republic">republic</a></td></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"></td></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row"><div style="text-indent:-0.9em;margin-left:1.2em;font-weight:normal;">•&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/President_of_Haiti" title="President of Haiti">President</a> </div></th><td><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jovenel_Mo%C3%AFse" title="Jovenel Moïse">Jovenel Moïse</a></td></tr><tr class="mergedrow"><th scope="row"><div style="text-indent:-0.9em;margin-left:1.2em;font-weight:normal;">•&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Haiti" title="Prime Minister of Haiti">Prime Minister</a> </div></th><td><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_Joute" class="mw-redirect" title="Joseph Joute">Joseph Joute</a></td></tr><tr style="display:none"><td colspan="2">
