<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Culture">Culture</span></h2>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Main article: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Culture_of_Haiti" title="Culture of Haiti">Culture of Haiti</a></div>
